OL,3,CRoger Hunt's 1966 World Cup shirt
OL,4,Ctipped to sell for thousands
OL,6,FA shirt worn by Roger Hunt during
OL,7,FEngland's quest for the 1966 World Cup
OL,8,Fis estimated to fetch up to #8,000
OL,9,Fwhen it is sold at auction.
OL,11,FThe striker - who played the majority
OL,12,Fof his career with Liverpool - wore
OL,13,Fthe long-sleeved white shirt against
OL,14,FFrance in a group game on July 20 as
OL,15,Fhe scored both goals in a 2-0 win.
OL,17,FHunt was part of the team that later
OL,18,Flifted the World Cup when England beat
OL,19,FWest Germany 4-2 at Wembley Stadium.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
