FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784130494
OL,3,CRoger Hunt's 1966 World Cup shirt
OL,4,Ctipped to sell for thousands
OL,6,FHe played in every game during the
OL,7,Ftournament and scored three times to
OL,8,Fhelp England out of their group.
OL,10,FThe forward, who played the majority
OL,11,Fof his career with Liverpool, won 34
OL,12,FEngland caps and scored 18
OL,13,Finternational goals.
OL,15,FHe died in 2021 at the age of 83.
OL,17,FThe signed shirt will go under the
OL,18,Fhammer at Henry Aldridge & Son
OL,19,Fauctioneers in Devizes, Wiltshire, on
OL,20,FSaturday, 18 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
