FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784130494
OL,3,CRoger Hunt's 1966 World Cup shirt
OL,4,Ctipped to sell for thousands
OL,6,FAuctioneer Andrew Aldridge said: "In
OL,7,Fthis most important of World Cup weeks
OL,8,Fwhere England could end 60 years of
OL,9,Fhurt, we are delighted to be offering
OL,10,FRoger Hunt's match-used shirt from the
OL,11,FFrance group game where he scored
OL,12,Ftwice.
OL,14,F"With exceptional provenance it is a
OL,15,Ftruly tangible link to the last time
OL,16,FEngland won the World Cup."
OL,26,@nD@bOUvD@AOUxD@[OU
