PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784130494
OL,3,CRoger Hunt's 1966 World Cup shirt
OL,4,Ctipped to sell for thousands
OL,6,FRoger Hunt spent most of his National
OL,7,FService time in the Devizes area, even
OL,8,Fplaying for Devizes Town during his
OL,9,Ftenure, and was lodging with the
OL,10,Fvendor's family most weekends.
OL,12,FThey became lifelong friends, visiting
OL,13,Fon regular occasions, and the shirt
OL,14,Fwas given to the father after the
OL,15,FWorld Cup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
