OL,3,CRoger Hunt's 1966 World Cup shirt
OL,4,Ctipped to sell for thousands
OL,6,FAlso included in the lot are copies of
OL,7,Fphotographs, one taken of Hunt with
OL,8,Fthe vendor when she was a child,
OL,9,Fanother with the father, and a third
OL,10,Fin more recent times in the vendor's
OL,11,Fgarden.
